<Layout title="Stores" description="In-game store priorities and real money value guide for Last War: Survival.">
  <h1>Stores</h1>
  <p>In-game stores (Alliance Store, Black Market, Season Shop, VIP) have clear priority orders. Always buy the things that directly power your main squad first.</p>

  <h2>Real Money Value (Honest Take)</h2>
  <p>Monthly card and battle pass are generally the best value for consistent players. Big packs are for whales or specific high-value events. Never feel pressured — the game is very playable as low spender or F2P with good discipline.</p>
</Layout>